items.title: Sox rally in 9th, remain 3 up with 7-run 15th
items.summary: The Red Sox's wild 13-6 win over the Rays on Friday night at Tropicana Field had a little bit of everything -- including a lot of heart by both teams, tucked away in its 15 innings.

items.title: Porcello seeks better fate vs. Cobb, Rays
items.summary: Veteran right-handers Rick Porcello and Alex Cobb match up again after last week's tilt in Fenway Park, squaring off on the Tropicana Field mound Saturday as the Red Sox try to boost their postseason hopes while dampening the Rays' October plans.
